Package: sentenceR
Title: Langauge-agnostic setence tokenizer with UDPipe back end
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Michal",
           family = "Mochtak",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "mochtak@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5598-5642"))
Description: sentenceR is a language agnostic utility designed for sentence tokenization of a raw text. Using the UDPipe POS tagging pipeline, the package automatically extracts sentences with their appropriate indexes. The package works with any of the 100+ language models natively provided by UDPipe package (see https://github.com/bnosac/udpipe).
